# Control API

Run locally:

```powershell
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\python -m pip install -e .[dev]
.\.venv\Scripts\python -m uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

Default local database:

- `sqlite:///./data/app.db`

Key endpoints:

- `GET /api/admin/system-settings`
- `POST /api/runtime/route-message`
- `GET /api/runtime/health`
